paragraphs.title: Import pandas, numpy, matplotlib
paragraphs.text:
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt; plt.rcdefaults()
plt.switch_backend('agg')
import seaborn as sns
sns.set(style="whitegrid", color_codes=True)
import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings("ignore", category=FutureWarning)
warnings.filterwarnings("ignore", message="divide by zero encountered") 
warnings.filterwarnings("ignore", message="invalid value encountered")

paragraphs.title: Passenger status (Alive/Dead) against Passenger Class
paragraphs.text:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt; plt.rcdefaults()
plt.switch_backend('agg')
titanic['survived'] = titanic['Survived'].map({1:'Alive', 0:'Dead'}) 
ax = sns.countplot(x = 'Pclass', hue = 'survived', palette = 'Set1', data = titanic)
ax.set(title = 'Passenger status (Alive/Dead) against Passenger Class', 
       xlabel = 'Passenger Class', ylabel = 'Total')

z.show(plt, width='600px')

paragraphs.title: Survived split over Age , Fare and Pclass
paragraphs.text:
g = sns.FacetGrid(titanic, hue="Survived", col="Pclass", margin_titles=True,
                  palette={1:"seagreen", 0:"gray"})
g=g.map(plt.scatter, "Fare", "Age",edgecolor="w").add_legend()

z.show(plt, width='700px')

paragraphs.title: How many first, second, and third class passengers are in our sample?
paragraphs.text:
fg = sns.FacetGrid(titanic, hue="Pclass", aspect=3, palette="BuPu_d")
fg.map(sns.kdeplot, "Age", shade=True)
fg.set(xlim=(0, 80))

z.show(plt,  width='400px')

paragraphs.title: Distribution of Passengers per Sex and Pclass
paragraphs.text:
fg = sns.FacetGrid(titanic, col="Sex", row="Pclass", hue="Sex", size=2.5, aspect=2.5, palette="OrRd_d")
fg.map(sns.kdeplot, "Age", shade=True)
fg.map(sns.rugplot, "Age")
sns.despine(left=True)
fg.set(xlim=(0, 80))

z.show(plt, width='600px')

paragraphs.title: How did age interact with sex ?
paragraphs.text:
age_bins = [15, 30, 45, 60]
sns.lmplot("Age", "Survived", titanic, hue="Sex", palette="OrRd_d", x_bins=age_bins, logistic=True).set(xlim=(0, 80))
           
z.show(plt,  width='600px')

paragraphs.title: How did age interact with class?
paragraphs.text:
age_bins = [15, 30, 45, 60]
sns.lmplot("Age", "Survived", titanic, hue="Pclass",
           palette="BuPu_d", x_bins=age_bins, logistic=True).set(xlim=(0, 80))
           
z.show(plt,  width='500px')
